featureboard.Text_1: Ka a nụ olu gị! Ị kwenyere na anyị kwesịrị ịmepụta atụmatụ ma ọ bụ ahụhụ? Pịa bọtịnụ iji kwado ya.
featureboard.Text_2: Chọrọ ka anyị mepụta atụmatụ ọhụrụ? Kọwaa ya n'okpuru.
featureboard.Text_3: Kwa izu, anyị na-amalite imepe atụmatụ kacha elu nke ndị obodo rịọrọ. Ego niile enyere na-aga maka ebumnuche ahụ, na-enye anyị ohere ime ka ngwa ahụ ka mma.
featureboard.Text_4: A na-eji ego niile enyere aka kwụọ ụgwọ mmepe anyị.
featureboard.Text_5: Ị nwere echiche maka njirimara ma ọ bụ bugfix nke ịchọrọ ka anyị mee mana ahụbeghị ka ndị ọzọ gbakwunyere? Kọwaa ya n'okpuru:

Options.text: $130 Chọgharịa wee kesaa ọtụtụ puku memes {{1}}

featureboard.FeatureDescription: Kọwaa otu onye ọzọ nwere ike isi mepụtaghachi ahụhụ ị na-ahụ, ma ọ bụ kọwapụta nke ọma atụmatụ ịchọrọ ịrụ.
